Vlad only had time to witness her efficiency. She had proceeded with 
definite speed that had not allowed him to raise a protest. He felt 
the sedative run inside him, mixing with his partly-human metabolism 
and sending him in a dreamless sleep in no time. He was knocked out 
for a few hours at the very least.
